Will Hatton has made a career out of travelling the globe as The Broke Backpacker . 
  The 26-year-old British backpacker spends only $100 a week on all of his expenses . 
  He picks up odd jobs wherever he goes and records his adventures on his blog . 
  He has visited nearly 50 countries over the last seven years . 
  Mr Hatton says he has been robbed on three occasions . 
  He also tried to work at a travel agency but failed . 
 